Package: forecastcalibration
Type: Package
Title: Testing Whether a Forecast Distribution is Calibrated
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Fabian Krueger, with contributions by Malte Knueppel
Maintainer: Fabian Krueger <fabian.krueger83@gmail.com>
Description: Covers univariate and multivariate forecast distributions. Implements the
    tests by Berkowitz (2001), Knueppel (2015) and Knueppel et al (2022+). 
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.1
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.5), magrittr, sandwich, scoringRules
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
